This template is an implementation of the image gallery script written by http://www.outcut.de/MooFlow
It uses mootools 1.2 and might not be compatiable with templates dependent upon the older version of mootools.
The following code can be added to the bottom of your joomla template to remove conflicts.

$address = JRequest::getVar('option');
if($address == 'com_maianmedia'){
   include_once(JPATH_SITE.DS.'components'.DS.'com_maianmedia'.DS.'templates'.DS.'mooflow'.DS.'behavior.php');
   MY_Behavior::mootoolsFix();
}

Ensure you use the PHP enclosing tags when needed.
